{"tid":1516093,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"支為慘了！新旗艦 Mate 30 將成第一支被 Android 放生的手機","createTime":"2019-08-29T12:17:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T13:24:32.000Z","uid":32511,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"174065643a26a088aef1b3affba09a2e7d404eb9","tid":1516093,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:17:49.000Z","msg":"華為慘了！據外媒報導，儘管美國政府再度給予華為 90 天緩衝期，卻只限於已上市的機款，意味即將發表的 Mate 30 系列，將成為第一支被 Android 放生的手機！<br />\n <br />\n《路透社》報導，由於美國商務部工業安全局（BIS）對華為下達的禁令，Google 證實不會提供 Mate 30 完整 Android 支援。目前只有舊機款，仍能持續獲得 Google 官方第一手的服務、支援，包含軟體與更新，時間只到今年 11 月 19 日。由於 Mate 30 預計於今年九月才會正式發表，因此並不在許可名單內。<br />\n <br />\n受惠於 Android 的開源性質，華為 Mate 30 仍舊能使用 Android 系統，但 Google 服務生態將會受到影響，宛如閹割版 Android 系統，包含 Play Store、Gmail、Chrome 都不能預載，也無法在第一時間獲得 Google 的更新支援，安全性與功能都會大打折扣。<br />\n <br />\n華為已經率先發表自家研發的鴻蒙 OS，並聲稱得以在一夜之間取代 Android，但在中國以外，Google 仍是消費者重度倚賴的 App 服務，縱使藉由瀏覽器與其他方式取代部分App，但恐怕也難掩 Mate 30 系列的致命缺點。<br />\n <br />\n不僅是 Google 放生華為，所有總部位於美國的企業，包含臉書、推特、IG，Mate 30 也都必須遵從禁令，禁止提供華為相關服務與支援。"},{"pid":"4314c868dfcba85d6d42ca1abb583be2a12f3602","tid":1516093,"uid":40356,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:18:49.000Z","msg":"愛中國 用國貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9453749b68bd3713fcbe6d6faf70c2caeb952da8","tid":1516093,"uid":278973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:19:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25f10f04580ec1e3af3f9407bfdf0733a9ac5e60","tid":1516093,"uid":243380,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:21:50.000Z","msg":"乜原來大陸放生同香港相反意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"808af2a9aa09bedc3b63e66a83363204534b030e","tid":1516093,"uid":293673,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:24:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8c418cd829708553fe5636147b6730cc72479351","tid":1516093,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:24:24.000Z","msg":"鴻蒙出左未？"},{"pid":"c0c34ccaeedff40fe4f2ae8d1a1de10917fb1102","tid":1516093,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:26:26.000Z","msg":"冇ANDROID真係狗都唔買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac4e5b46be4b848843625522c0ce69c069584ddd","tid":1516093,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:30:38.000Z","msg":"點解係要乜鳩都痴外國勢力，唔係話自己好撚勁好撚先進架咩？"},{"pid":"9f4a7c2ddb10cb4762e36b6aaecf6608bbd0847f","tid":1516093,"uid":92836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:30:57.000Z","msg":"毋忘聽日830香港重光紀念日。<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><em>830中環見<br />\n830中環見<br />\n830中環見</em></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/96PXdYs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F96PXdYs.jpg&h=2d869ee7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4KF8LYC.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4KF8LYC.gif&h=64c0bd73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n［行動Post］ 830 感謝勇武暨重光紀念日行動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1511085\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1511085</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"836710f684808c49d29aee5daf4c97b557a04b85","tid":1516093,"uid":292737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25f10f04580ec1e3af3f9407bfdf0733a9ac5e60","tid":1516093,"uid":243380,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:21:50.000Z","msg":"乜原來大陸放生同香港相反意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T13:24:32.000Z","msg":"係台灣，台灣先會用「一支手機」，大陸係「一台手機」"}]}